# Agent Policy for kin.rag.wtf
# Formal declaration of agent usage rights for this portfolio site.
# Last updated: 2026-04-16

## Permitted Uses
- Indexing and crawling all public pages for search and discovery
- Extracting and summarising content for informational purposes
- Citing content with proper attribution and a link to the source page
- Accessing the JSON API endpoints (/api/*.json) for structured data retrieval
- Reading /llms.txt and /llms-full.txt for LLM-optimised consumption
- Using the portfolio data to answer questions about Lim Chee Kin's professional background, projects, and articles

## Prohibited Uses
- Reproducing the full site content verbatim without attribution
- Misrepresenting the site owner's views, credentials, or affiliations
- Automated form submission (the contact form is for human use only)
- Scraping for AI training datasets without explicit written permission from the site owner

## Rate Limits
- No hard rate limits are enforced, but agents should respect the Cache-Control headers on API responses (max-age=3600)
- Use conditional GET requests with If-None-Match / ETag headers to avoid redundant fetches
- Please be courteous with request frequency; avoid hammering endpoints

## Data Freshness
- All content is generated at build time. The Last-Modified header on any page reflects the last deployment date.
- Subscribe to /rss.xml for content change notifications.

